Training leverages large-scale video datasets (e.g., Kinetics, AVA) to transfer temporal knowledge to static image inference. Applications span domains with limited video access—historical photos, medical imaging, robotics—and advance AI’s ability to infer dynamics from static scenes. A key open question is whether to prioritize a **general framework** or focus initially on a specific domain like surveillance or sports.
